{"tid":1967070,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"IG單野，可唔可以去間Fact Check公司投訴施壓？","createTime":"2020-04-10T15:44:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-10T15:51:55.000Z","uid":211994,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3218218885f2f0468f1a9a45d7a1b5c35f260f64","tid":1967070,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T15:44:08.000Z","msg":"唔知可唔可行，不過大家一齊試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢主要都係話因為幅相執過嚟，所以可能會有誤導成分<br />\n咁如果我地證明到<span style=\"color: red;\">執相只係修飾，事實上真係有咁多人去遊行</span>嘅話，會唔會可以解除到佢個限制呢？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hDaG5fc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhDaG5fc.png&h=59d0ece5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n搵到間公司嘅Twitter，有冇英文好嘅手足可以幫下拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MtLzFOy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMtLzFOy.png&h=ac59ecf2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行動目的：<br />\n證明張相冇誤導成分<br />\n<br />\n方法：<br />\n搵當日遊行嘅照片（最好嚟自各大傳媒）去證明，個日真係好多人遊行<br />\n作者攞返張原圖出嚟做證明<br />\n<br />\n大家一齊討論下，係咁tag instagram真係冇咩用"},{"pid":"be454b73590cd74b63554f5d7473dafb60739065","tid":1967070,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T15:44:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dd951c066a38bb03976906aff86b73cf883476c5","tid":1967070,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T15:44:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4ea30dfcd209255344d8040c9e7c4ae891656a69","tid":1967070,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T15:45:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"feb4690b79744babbda9f6a7d02a8b7a77b14990","tid":1967070,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T15:45:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0563468e6907